---
import ZhLayout from '../../../../layouts/ZhLayout.astro';
---

<ZhLayout
  title="自动化设备 | DGSDK 史帝克"
  description="史帝克定制工业自动化设备：扩散板清洗检验生产线、机器人自动上下料清洗机、偏光片吸收轴角度测量系统，提升工厂生产效率。"
  canonical="https://www.dg-sdk.com/zh/products/automation"
>
  <section
    class="products-hero"
    style="background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18)), url('/assets/img/automation/product-a.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;"
  >
    <div class="container products-hero-inner">
      <span class="products-hero-kicker">史帝克产品系列</span>
      <h1>自动化设备</h1>
      <p>
        定制工业自动化系统，提升工作流程效率、减少人工操作、优化生产节拍，适用于电子、光学和精密制造行业。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="products-overview-section">
    <div class="container products-overview-layout">
      <aside class="products-sidebar">
        <div class="products-sidebar-box">
          <h3>产品分类</h3>
          <a href="/zh/products">所有产品</a>
          <a href="/zh/products/static-eliminator">静电消除系统</a>
          <a href="/zh/products/cleaning-machine">工业清洁机</a>
          <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts">精密加工零件</a>
          <a href="/zh/products/automation" class="active-category">自动化设备</a>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <div class="products-main">
        <section class="apple-product-section">
          <div class="apple-card-grid">
            <a href="/products/automation/product-a" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/automation/product-a.jpg" alt="扩散板清洗检验生产线" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">自动化</span>
              <h3>扩散板清洗检验生产线</h3>
              <p>集清洗、检验和连续传送为一体的高效自动化生产线。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/automation/product-b" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/automation/product-b.jpg" alt="机器人自动上下料清洗机" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">自动化</span>
              <h3>机器人自动上下料清洗机</h3>
              <p>机器人集成，自动上下料，减少人工操作，清洗效率大幅提升。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/products/automation/product-c" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/automation/product-c.jpg" alt="偏光片吸收轴角度测量系统" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">自动化</span>
              <h3>偏光片吸收轴角度测量系统</h3>
              <p>高精度偏光片吸收轴角度自动检测，满足严格的品质管控要求。</p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="related-categories-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="related-cat-title">完善您的生产线</h2>
      <p class="related-cat-desc">自动化设备与清洁机和静电消除系统配合使用，可实现完整的生产线解决方案：</p>
      <div class="related-cat-grid">
        <a href="/zh/products/cleaning-machine" class="related-cat-card">
          <img src="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/polarizer-cleaner.jpg" alt="工业清洁机" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="related-cat-info">
            <h3>工业清洁机</h3>
            <p>各类精密制造应用的表面清洁解决方案。</p>
            <span class="related-cat-link">查看产品 →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/zh/products/static-eliminator" class="related-cat-card">
          <img src="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-g.jpg" alt="静电消除系统" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="related-cat-info">
            <h3>静电消除系统</h3>
            <p>将静电控制无缝集成到自动化生产线中。</p>
            <span class="related-cat-link">查看产品 →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts" class="related-cat-card">
          <img src="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/precision-bearing-bracket-cnc-milled.jpg" alt="精密加工零件" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="related-cat-info">
            <h3>精密加工零件</h3>
            <p>用于自动化系统集成的定制CNC零件。</p>
            <span class="related-cat-link">查看产品 →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ZhLayout>
